article:
The following is a 'list of Internet top-level domains (TLDs)'. The top-level
domain article provides the background information.

The official list of all top-level domains is maintained by the Internet
Assigned Numbers Authority (IANA). [http://data.iana.org/TLD/tlds-alpha-by-
domain.txt IANA maintained list of top-level domains]

A number of proposed top-level domains are under consideration by ICANN/IANA.
